dct_description_sm: Norway. Norges Geografiske Oppmåaling. Alternate title: Skikart, Lillehammer omland. Relief is shown by form lines. Height is shown by spot heights, and depth by soundings. In upper right corner: Omlandskart 1:50,000. Surveyed 1938-40. 1957
